# Physics Core Rules

- SI units everywhere: meters, seconds, kilograms, newtons, volts, amps.
- Pure functions preferred. Deterministic given same inputs.
- Default integration: semi-implicit Euler. Document if using different method.
- Fixed timestep (e.g., `dt = 1/120`). Variable dt only in outer loop.
- All physics classes must be testable without DOM or React.
